{"type": "article", "id": 10348, "title": "Cloud Vase 花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-03T08:32:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235526083s54tTdOaMrDQX.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">法国设计师 Ronan 和 Erwan Bouroullec 最近配合他们的<a href=\"http://www.jrp-ringier.com/pages/index.php?id_r=4&amp;id_t=&amp;id_p=15&amp;id_b=2502&amp;search=bouroullec&amp;page=1&amp;total=3\" target=\"_blank\">画册 Drawing </a>的出版设计了一款叫做 “Cloud Vase” 的花瓶，不过他们可没有听起来这么浪漫，实际上看上去还有点儿像蜂窝煤，但搭配上植物居然看起来十分和谐。花瓶一共有四个部分，各个部分高低不一，倒也错落有致。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355233PKdNXM5bmCULqDs.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355247O9t8m3QehAX1BL5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355246wjfmuhP54oXVQI1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235524ZfN0gvzFGmIdYe9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355257Z0IJRpmPdvXx3hi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}